Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.70,0:00:07.65,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Ya, halo?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.65,0:00:08.57,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,Hai!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.59,0:00:11.63,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Ah, Kayama. Sudah lama, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.63,0:00:14.57,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kehidupan sebagai guru?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.38,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,Sangat memuaskan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.38,0:00:19.47,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,Muridnya imut dan bersemangat,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.47,0:00:21.82,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,kurikulumnya juga bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.82,0:00:25.58,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,Selalu ada hal baru\Nsaat berada di sisi pengajar.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.06,0:00:27.96,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,Sekolah memang menyenangkan, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.96,0:00:30.20,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,Rasanya tempatku memang di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.20,0:00:31.24,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.24,0:00:33.79,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Secara pribadi, aku kurang suka.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.79,0:00:36.05,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Tak ada kenangan indah soal sekolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.05,0:00:40.07,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,Aduh, jangan pilih-pilih\Nsuka atau tidak. Ini pekerjaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.07,0:00:42.52,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Tapi itu bukan pekerjaanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.74,0:00:44.83,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,Akan jadi pekerjaanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.83,0:00:47.10,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,Menjadi guru Prodi Pahlawan SMA U.A.,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.10,0:00:50.20,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,almamater kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.20,0:00:51.91,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Tiba-tiba bicara apa, sih?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.19,0:00:53.69,dialog,Mic,0,0,0,,Ye!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.69,0:00:57.00,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,Semester depan, Yamada juga\Nsudah dipastikan masuk U.A.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.00,0:00:59.34,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,Tinggal kau yang belum putuskan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.34,0:01:01.83,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Jangan anggap kami satu paket.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.83,0:01:06.00,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, aku tak pernah bilang\Nmau jadi guru.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.00,0:01:08.19,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,Yamada bilang,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.19,0:01:12.66,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,"Dia tipe yang tak bisa putuskan apa pun\Ntanpa dorongan orang lain."
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.66,0:01:18.21,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Sampaikan padanya, "Dia itu tipe orang\Nyang cuma bicara hal tak penting."
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.96,0:01:25.35,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,Aku juga merasa kau sedang menghindar
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.76,0:01:27.61,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,dari hal yang benar-benar penting.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.83,0:01:31.40,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Aku ralat.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.57,0:01:34.61,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,"Kalian tipe orang yang cuma\Nbicara hal tak penting."
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.77,0:01:36.45,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,Hei, dengar.\NAyo bicara serius sebentar...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.48,0:01:38.58,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Aku sedang patroli.\NPermisi.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.00,0:01:42.95,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Benar-benar tidak rasional.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.16,0:01:48.00,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Baiklah, waktunya bekerja.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.06,0:03:34.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan tindas yang lemah!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.27,0:03:38.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak kecil atau anak kucing juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.40,0:03:41.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Awas kau, si tudung merah kecil!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.67,0:03:45.25,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Aku akan jadi umpan,\Nkau bawa kucingnya dan kabur!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.25,0:03:46.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.06,0:03:51.98,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Hei, hei! Sini, sini!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau juga kelihatan lemah!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.94,0:03:56.46,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Sini, sini!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.46,0:04:13.55,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, Eraser!\NAku sangat terbantu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.96,0:04:17.98,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Apa yang kau lakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.30,0:04:20.11,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Jadi begini...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.60,0:04:22.95,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.95,0:04:24.66,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.10,0:04:28.51,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Aku sedang pikirkan caranya,\Ntiba-tiba dia datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.54,0:04:30.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?! Kucing?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.66,0:04:32.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kutindas!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.83,0:04:34.06,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Lalu dia menyerang.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.06,0:04:36.11,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Kasus sederhana.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.70,0:04:39.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah menolongku.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.17,0:04:41.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong jaga kucingnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.78,0:04:44.01,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Hati-hati pulangnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.86,0:04:53.06,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Halo, ini Pahlawan Pro, Eraser Head.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.06,0:04:56.73,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Pelaku penyerangan sudah kutangkap,\Nmohon segera diamankan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.00,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.00,0:05:02.97,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Lokasi sudah kukirim via GPS,\Nsilakan dicek.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.97,0:05:06.71,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Sepertinya akan hujan deras.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.36,0:05:22.20,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Terus, kucingnya mau diapakan?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.20,0:05:26.79,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Eh... yah, sementara kubawa pulang dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.79,0:05:28.33,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Kau akan memeliharanya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.33,0:05:30.51,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Itu belum kuputuskan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.69,0:05:33.83,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Harus beri makan\Ndan bersihkan kotoran tiap hari.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.98,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Bisakah kau melatihnya dengan benar?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.18,0:05:38.78,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Vaksin dan steril itu wajib.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.78,0:05:42.19,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Kalau sakit,\Nbiayanya lebih mahal daripada manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.07,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Kau masih mahasiswa, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.07,0:05:47.41,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Kalau masa depanmu berubah,\Napa kau masih bisa merawatnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.96,0:05:51.70,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Kucing bisa hidup sampai 20 tahun.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.70,0:05:54.21,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Bisa bertanggung jawab sampai akhir?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.21,0:05:57.92,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Yah, 20 tahun memang susah dibayangkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.92,0:06:00.40,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Kalau tak bisa pelihara,\Njangan sembarangan bawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.40,0:06:02.71,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Kembalikan ke tempat asalnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.90,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Apa kau tidak suka kucing?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.94,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Bukan soal suka atau tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.94,0:06:11.81,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Dari tadi kau sama sekali\Ntidak melihat kucingnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.23,0:06:17.18,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Untuk apa terbawa perasaan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.40,0:06:22.53,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Kalau tak bisa tanggung jawab,\Njangan ikut campur sejak awal.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.53,0:06:25.31,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Kau dingin sekali, Eraser.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.18,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.23,0:06:34.75,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Aku hanya tahu batasku.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.70,0:06:45.21,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Aku bukan All Might.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.76,0:06:49.65,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Ada batas kekuatan\Nyang bisa dimiliki satu orang.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.66,0:06:55.85,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Apalagi aku belum bisa dibilang\N"setengah matang".
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.63,0:07:06.91,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Sejak kecil, aku selalu berpikir begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.46,0:07:11.45,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Entah aku menginginkannya atau tidak...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.03,0:07:19.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau?\NLupa bawa payung?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.12,0:07:22.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebentar lagi apel pagi.\NGanti baju sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.80,0:07:26.38,dialog - atas,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Tak apa-apa.\NSuasana hatiku lagi begini.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.66,0:07:30.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bapak tak tahu suasana hati macam apa,\Ntapi nanti kau masuk angin.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jaga kesehatan juga kewajiban murid.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagian dari jalan menuju pahlawan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.69,0:07:36.75,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Ya...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.66,0:07:39.94,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Pahlawan atau jalan semacam itu
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.94,0:07:42.73,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,sama sekali tak terbayang olehku.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.43,0:07:48.65,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Aku tak berdaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.65,0:07:53.00,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Keluar, deh!\NOmongan negatif khas Shota Aizawa!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.00,0:07:56.75,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Pagi-pagi sudah putus asa, HEY YO!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.66,0:08:00.00,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Seru, nih, ayo dengar sekali lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.00,0:08:04.48,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Aizawa berkata, "Aku tak berdaya."
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.63,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Berisik.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.02,0:08:11.00,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Orang yang asyik!\NNegatif! Pasif! Pesimistis!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.00,0:08:12.30,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Menyebalkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.80,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Hei, hei, hei, Hizashi!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.96,dialog - atas,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Sedang apa kau, mengganggu Shota?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.96,0:08:20.45,dialog - atas,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Tidak boleh, tidak baik itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.45,0:08:22.18,dialog - atas,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Aku juga mau ikut!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Shirakumo!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.84,0:08:25.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau masuk lewat mana?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.80,0:08:28.40,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Siap menjawab! Jendela lantai tiga!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.59,0:08:30.78,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Quirk-ku, Cloud!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.40,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Praktis buat bergerak!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.40,0:08:36.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Quirk atau bukan, masuklah lewat pintu!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.51,0:08:37.78,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Siap, Pak!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.20,0:08:41.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat duduk! Bapak mau absen!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.66,0:08:43.25,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.54,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Pinjam handuk, dong!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.44,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Aku basah kuyup!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.44,0:08:48.62,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Ye!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.62,0:08:50.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepatlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.81,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Oh iya, Shota, Shota!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.23,0:08:55.84,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Payung ini punyamu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.05,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.21,0:08:58.71,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Kau menjatuhkannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.47,0:09:04.06,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Shirakumo, di bawah payung ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.06,0:09:07.14,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Hei, hei, hei, Oboro!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.14,0:09:09.31,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau lepas semua?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.77,0:09:12.90,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Habisnya, celana dalam basah itu tidak enak!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tutupi sedikit, dong!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.17,0:09:16.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mesum kau, ya?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.16,0:09:19.00,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Hadirin sekalian, tak perlu cemas!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.00,0:09:20.81,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Saksikan dengan tenang.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.23,0:09:24.57,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Aplikasi elegan Quirk Cloud...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.57,0:09:26.41,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,estetika di ambang batas terlihat...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.76,0:09:28.63,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,tapi tak terlihat!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.81,0:09:32.92,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Dan di dalamnya\Nada makhluk yang sangat imut.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.92,0:09:35.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei! Sudah!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.18,0:09:36.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada cewek di sini!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shirakumo parah!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mati saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.51,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Tara!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.73,0:09:51.78,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Hei, Oboro, kau memungut sesuatu lagi, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.06,0:09:57.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik, absen! Mulai dari siswa laki-laki.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.74,0:09:58.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aizawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.94,0:10:00.33,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Hadir.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.33,0:10:02.58,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Hujannya berhenti.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.79,0:10:03.67,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Oizuchi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.20,0:10:06.05,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Bahkan tahap "setengah matang"\Npun belum kucapai.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.67,0:10:04.63,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.21,0:10:06.34,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Katasugi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.34,0:10:07.21,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.59,0:10:08.34,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Kuga.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.85,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Aku tak merasa akan pernah mencapainya,\Nkapan pun, di mana pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.34,0:10:09.38,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Hadir.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.22,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Sarudo.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.22,0:10:12.46,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.46,0:10:13.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shirakumo.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.76,0:10:15.06,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Hadir!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.06,0:10:18.11,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Pada akhirnya, aku bahkan tak bisa\Nmenyelamatkan seekor kucing.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.63,0:10:19.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tendo.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.80,0:10:20.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.78,0:10:22.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Niragi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.00,0:10:23.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.17,0:10:24.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fujimi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.16,0:10:25.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ihihi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.37,0:10:26.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mushimori.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.35,0:10:27.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hadir...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.44,0:10:28.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yamada.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.43,0:10:29.78,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Ye!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.26,0:10:31.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yamada, berisik.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.83,0:10:35.94,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Sikap pasrah itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.36,0:10:37.85,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Pada musim panas tahun kedua SMA,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.50,0:10:43.11,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,perlahan mulai berubah.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.10,0:11:01.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seperti biasa, sebagian besar murid akan\Nmemulai magang pada libur musim panas.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.22,0:11:04.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski pemagang, kalian akan terjun\Nlangsung ke lapangan Pahlawan Pro.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.93,0:11:07.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Teguhkan tekad kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.07,0:11:08.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan juga,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.30,0:11:12.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang hingga kini belum dapat tempat magang,\Nmulailah merasa sedikit panik.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.69,0:11:13.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aizawa,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shirakumo,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yamada.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.65,0:11:19.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian paham?\NIni soal kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.77,0:11:20.52,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.54,0:11:21.49,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Siap!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.49,0:11:22.82,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Ye!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.26,0:11:25.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yamada, berisik.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.63,0:11:33.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, semua kumpul di lapangan\Nmengenakan kostum.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.63,0:11:38.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulai hari ini, sementara kita akan\Nlatihan praktik gabungan dengan Kelas B.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.70,0:11:44.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Periksa kelebihan dan kekurangan\Nmasing-masing.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.16,0:11:47.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang unggul,\Nperkuat kelemahan sebelum magang.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.07,0:11:52.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang tertinggal, mantapkan gambaran\Nmasa depan kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.56,0:11:55.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertama, latihan tempur satu lawan satu!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.71,0:11:57.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulai!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.96,0:12:00.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasangan ditentukan secara acak.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.24,0:12:03.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bertarunglah dengan memanfaatkan\Nkeunikan kalian!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.87,0:12:09.04,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Eh! Ups!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.72,0:12:20.09,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Ye!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Latihan penyelamatan!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.87,0:12:42.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penanganan bencana adalah kerja tim!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.75,0:12:45.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jalankan peran kalian dengan tepat!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.18,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Masih ada orang di sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.62,0:12:56.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pelajaran tari!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.50,0:13:00.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pahlawan adalah wajah yang mewakili\Nberbagai posisi di masyarakat!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.43,0:13:04.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tanpa popularitas, tidak akan ada permintaan\Ndan hidup kalian pasti sulit!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.14,0:13:07.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunjukkan diri kalian!\NRebut perhatian penonton!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.80,0:13:15.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana dengan tiga orang itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.31,0:13:17.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, yang belum dapat magang?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.26,0:13:21.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, Yamada seharusnya tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.65,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Ye!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.99,0:13:28.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Quirk "Voice" dia serbaguna. Bisa untuk\Nbertarung, penyelamatan, atau hiburan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.41,0:13:30.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia memang tertarik pada banyak hal.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.81,0:13:34.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Justru karena bisa segalanya,\Ndia sulit tentukan satu jalan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.97,0:13:38.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tipe yang nantinya akan jalani\Ndua atau tiga peran sekaligus.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.96,0:13:42.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shirakumo juga meski nilainya biasa,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.44,0:13:44.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,kepribadiannya ceria dan positif.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.77,0:13:45.59,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Hai!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.77,0:13:49.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bisa berjalan\Ndengan ritmenya sendiri di mana pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.75,0:13:52.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sisanya... Aizawa, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.13,0:13:55.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, dia juga sudah bekerja keras.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.75,0:14:01.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nilai praktik dan teorinya\Nselalu di atas rata-rata.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.27,0:14:06.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya saja... meski berjuang,\Nvisi masa depannya belum jelas.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.22,0:14:09.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama tujuannya belum jelas,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.01,0:14:12.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,kami tak bisa merekomendasikannya\Nke tempat magang.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.33,0:14:16.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin karena sifat Quirk\Nyang dia miliki sejak lahir...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.86,0:14:22.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, di latihan tempur\Nbeberapa hari lalu juga...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.81,dialog,Sensoji,0,0,0,,Menyebalkan, tahu, Aizawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.52,dialog,Sensoji,0,0,0,,Entah itu "Erasure" atau apa,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.52,0:14:39.23,dialog,Sensoji,0,0,0,,tapi setelah kau hapus Quirk orang,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.23,0:14:42.85,dialog,Sensoji,0,0,0,,lalu kau mainkan kain aneh itu\Nsambil membelit lawan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.16,0:14:50.75,dialog,Sensoji,0,0,0,,Kalau kau ikut campur,\Npertarungannya jadi hambar,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.40,dialog,Sensoji,0,0,0,,dan aku tidak bisa bersinar.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.40,0:14:59.55,dialog,Sensoji,0,0,0,,Ujung-ujungnya kalah gara-gara adu tinju.\NItu tak ada gunanya sama sekali!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.10,0:15:03.25,dialog,Sensoji,0,0,0,,Jangan pakai trik murahan begitu, dong!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.36,0:15:06.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Sensoji!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak apa-apa, Aizawa?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.91,0:15:13.18,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.20,0:15:15.85,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Mau bagaimana lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.50,0:15:19.31,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Beginilah Quirk-ku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.46,0:15:27.90,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Jujur saja, Erasure cuma Quirk\Nyang sedikit menghambat orang lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.90,0:15:30.36,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa lakukan apa pun sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.70,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Jelas tak bisa membuat orang lain senang.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.16,0:15:37.27,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Makanya aku tak benar-benar tahu apa\Nyang bisa kulakukan dengan Quirk ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.27,0:15:41.01,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,atau apa yang sebenarnya ingin kulakukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.36,0:15:46.84,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,\Ntinggal hambat penjahat saja, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.90,0:15:49.61,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Jadi fokus pada pertarungan?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.06,0:15:52.65,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Aku sulit membayangkannya, sih.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.23,0:15:57.26,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Pertarungan Quirk memang\Ntergantung kecocokan, tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.26,0:16:00.52,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Dengan Erasure milik Shota,\Nsiapa pun lawannya,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.52,0:16:03.40,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,kau bisa memaksanya jadi adu fisik murni.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.40,0:16:05.60,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Itu bakat.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.60,0:16:08.47,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Aku juga tak terlalu jago\Nbertarung tangan kosong.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.47,0:16:11.38,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Aku tak berdaya melawan musuh besar...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.63,0:16:14.77,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Hei. Tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.91,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Jangan kasih makanan orang ke kucing.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.91,0:16:18.54,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Tidak baik buat tubuhnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.25,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Oh, begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.46,0:16:24.55,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Untung aku bawa susu kucing ekstra.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.71,0:16:30.62,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Sejujurnya, aku juga menentang\Nmembawanya ke sekolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.62,0:16:34.11,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Tapi ditinggal di rumah juga\Nbikin khawatir, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.11,0:16:37.05,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Kalau di sekolah, Aizawa yang urus!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.55,0:16:40.77,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Soal buang airnya bagaimana?\NApa dia baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.77,0:16:44.02,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Biasanya di baju olahragaku, sih!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.77,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Oh! Dasar kucing nakal!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.16,0:16:49.68,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Jorok banget!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.68,0:16:51.83,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Latih yang benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.83,0:16:53.90,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Aduh, kalian bertiga.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.90,0:16:57.00,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Makan siang di tempat begini?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.00,0:17:00.41,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Oh, kakak kelas tahun ketiga...\NSenior Kayama!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.45,0:17:02.99,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Keren banget!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.99,0:17:05.40,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Atap sekolah adalah area terlarang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.00,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Kalian masuk sembarangan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.00,0:17:09.71,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Pelanggaran aturan seperti itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.91,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Terasa sangat masa muda, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.63,0:17:17.60,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Apa yang Senior lakukan di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.60,0:17:22.34,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Aku baru pulang magang,\Ntapi ada urusan administrasi sekolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.34,0:17:25.27,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Sekalian mampir ke sini,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.27,0:17:27.44,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,karena ini tempat favoritku.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.60,0:17:29.61,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Pelaku pelanggaran berulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.60,0:17:32.21,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, Senior...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.83,0:17:35.75,dialog - atas,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Kau tak pakai baju di balik mantel itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.06,0:17:38.70,dialog - atas,Kayama,0,0,0,,Ini kostumku.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.87,0:17:42.22,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Bahan baru yang tak terlihat orang bodoh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.22,0:17:44.71,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Mungkin versi cerita baju baru sang ratu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.71,0:17:45.96,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Oh, menyindir diri sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.96,0:17:49.64,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Untung aku bodoh!\NBajunya tidak kelihatan!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.64,0:17:53.59,dialog - atas,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Hore! Hore! Hore!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.86,0:17:53.11,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Dasar, kalian benar-benar tidak paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.76,0:17:56.15,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Berani sekaligus praktis.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.15,0:17:59.07,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Ini keindahan fungsional itu sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.07,0:18:04.89,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Desain ini hasil riset maksimal\Nuntuk mendukung Quirk dan aksiku!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.63,0:18:09.18,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Tak ada sedikit pun rasa malu di sini!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.63,0:18:12.98,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Menurutku, sedikit rasa malu\Njustru lebih baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.98,0:18:15.95,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Shota, jangan bicara yang tidak perlu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.70,0:18:21.46,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Hatimu yang kotor, yang menganggap\Nsesuatu yang indah itu cabul.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.46,0:18:25.16,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Yah, untuk sekarang wajar saja\Norang bilang begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.16,0:18:28.37,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Mungkin itu takdir orang\Nyang berjalan mendahului zaman.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.57,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Tapi tunggu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.60,0:18:34.17,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Satu tahun lagi,\Nakal sehat di Jepang akan berubah!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.17,0:18:36.05,dialog,N,0,0,0,,Sebagai catatan, setahun kemudian.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.05,0:18:41.11,dialog,N,0,0,0,,Dimulai pembahasan RUU tentang\NTingkat Eksposur Kostum Pahlawan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.60,0:18:44.58,dialog,N,0,0,0,,Hukum berubah lebih dulu\Ndaripada akal sehat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.30,0:18:47.05,dialog,Midnight,0,0,0,,Terlalu cepat, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.63,0:18:51.09,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Mengesampingkan diriku,\Nada apa dengan anak kucing itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.11,0:18:52.49,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Ah, ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.51,0:18:54.49,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Aku dan Shota yang menemukannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.49,0:18:57.36,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Meski begitu, jangan bawa ke sekolah, dong.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.36,0:18:59.15,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Sini, coba kulihat!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.04,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Ah, lembut banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.04,0:19:05.11,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Anak kucing ini datang dari mana, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.46,0:19:08.56,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Perutnya bulat, terus ngantuk, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.56,0:19:10.23,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Ini agak memalukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.23,0:19:11.96,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Kucing ini namanya siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.96,0:19:13.61,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Eh, itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.26,0:19:16.04,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Belum ditentukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.04,0:19:18.75,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, makanan favorit kalian apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.75,0:19:19.84,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Sushi!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.84,0:19:21.05,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Karaage!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.39,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Tidak ada yang khusus.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.56,0:19:26.43,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Kalau dari pilihan itu, aku pilih sushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.02,0:19:33.85,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Sushi kecil ini kelas premium, ya.\NAkan kumakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.86,0:19:38.53,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Kami lagi cari pemilik buat dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.53,0:19:41.91,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Sayang sekali, tapi setelah lulus\Naku akan pindah dari rumah orang tuaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.91,0:19:43.74,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Jadi tak punya waktu untuk mengurusnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.74,0:19:47.17,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Katanya kalau tinggal sendiri sambil\Nmemelihara kucing, umur nikah bisa mundur.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.17,0:19:49.50,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Dia khawatir soal itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.50,0:19:52.21,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Jadi aku tak bisa menampungnya lama-lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.21,0:19:54.98,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Cepat cari pengadopsi yang tepat, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.10,0:19:58.98,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Ujung-ujungnya tetap dia yang pelihara.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.98,0:20:00.35,dialog,Yamada,0,0,0,,Ye!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.26,0:20:05.27,dialog - atas,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Bukankah ini tidak bertanggung jawab?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.27,0:20:09.18,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Menyerahkan makhluk hidup begitu saja\Nkarena terbawa suasana.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.18,0:20:11.77,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Kalau Senior Kayama sih, pasti aman.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.83,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, sekarang bukan\Nwaktunya pelihara kucing.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.83,0:20:19.40,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Ya, soal magang.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.40,0:20:22.86,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Barusan kudengar Yamada\Njuga sudah dapat tempat.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.08,0:20:25.26,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Katanya tipe pertarungan...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.26,0:20:28.35,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Sekarang lagi dapat penjelasan\Ndi ruang guru.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.76,0:20:31.95,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Padahal dia tak terlalu\Nmerasa tipe petarung.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.30,0:20:35.79,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Dia memang punya acara radio web sendiri\Ndan selalu bicara.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.02,0:20:40.40,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Magang itu buat cari pengalaman\Nyang tak bisa didapat sendirian.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.40,0:20:44.15,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Kalau bertarung sendirian,\Nujung-ujungnya cuma jadi preman.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.80,0:20:48.96,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Oh, ketemu juga, klub bocah atap.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.96,0:20:50.78,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Ah, Senior Kayama!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.23,0:20:53.77,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah mengurus kucingnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.86,0:20:58.27,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Ini, Sushi hari ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.27,0:21:02.75,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Wah, pup-nya banyak, ya!\NPintar, pintar!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.20,0:21:05.25,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Menunjukkan itu saat orang lagi makan...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.25,0:21:08.25,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Kau khawatir\Nsoal latihan buang airnya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.25,0:21:10.79,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Jadi Senior datang\Ncuma buat tunjukkan video ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.79,0:21:15.50,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Bukan. Aku tahu tempat sempurna\Nuntuk anak yang tak punya tujuan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.70,0:21:19.23,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Kami tidak memungut\Nhewan telantar setiap hari.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.23,0:21:22.03,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Bukan itu.\NAku bicara soal magang.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.03,0:21:24.96,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Bos di kantorku bilang\Ndia akan mengurus kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.96,0:21:26.00,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.00,0:21:28.00,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Bos kantor Senior?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.00,0:21:30.97,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Bos dari agensi tempatku magang.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.00,0:21:35.95,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Perwakilan Office Purple Revolution.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.26,0:21:40.18,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Noble Hero, Highness Purple!\NOrang itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.00,0:21:42.35,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.00,0:21:44.35,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Bagaimana menurut kami...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.36,0:21:48.20,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Bukankah karakter orang ini agak intens?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.20,0:21:50.31,dialog,Kayama,0,0,0,,Oh, justru itulah kelebihannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.96,0:21:52.81,dialog,Shirakumo,0,0,0,,Be-Benarkah?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.84,0:23:28.05,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Dia bilang padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.40,0:23:32.05,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Sendirian mungkin mustahil,\Ntapi berdua kita bisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.01,0:23:35.25,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Selanjutnya, "Langit Kaca".
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.85,0:23:39.65,dialog,Aizawa,0,0,0,,Langit yang tertutup awan,\Nperlahan mulai cerah.
